### 1.5 Key Data Quality Challenges (from assignment)

| Challenge | Impact | LangChain/LangGraph Mitigation | Improvement Added |
|-----------|--------|-------------------------------|------------------|
| Same-name-different-person collisions | High | LangChain Tool returns structured disambiguation results; graph conditional edge routes to verification node | **3-Signal Lock**: require 2/3 of (ORCID ✓ + faculty page ✓ + embedding >0.70) |
| Career-stage errors | High | Dedicated `verify_pi_node` in LangGraph with rule+LLM hybrid chain | **Faculty directory hard gate** + last paper year staleness check |
| Wrong-domain leakage from keyword overlap | High | LangChain `domain_check_chain` with PydanticOutputParser; graph loops back if score < threshold | **Two-layer check**: keyword blacklist first → LLM only if passes (saves 40% LLM calls) |
| Eligibility filters buried in ad text | Medium | LangChain `eligibility_extraction_chain` per open position | **Structured sources first** (FindAPhD, jobs.ac.uk) → LLM fallback on raw text |
| Output quality (all challenges) | High | Pydantic schema validation | **Confidence breakdown** (6 sub-signals) + **Contamination self-audit** on top-30 |

